page.title: 14Local Events 7-14.7.85
page.content: A woman who claimed that her children were starving abandoned 2 puppies near the famous site of the Swanscombe Man, because she said she could not afford to keep them.An eminent geologist and his American colleague took charge of the dogs as the distressed mother hurried off without giving her name. The puppies will be destroyed in 7 days time unless somebody claims them. Northfleet Carnival was held on Saturday and there were many attractions including bands,majorettes and floats from local firms and organisations.A new game called Kabbadi is hoped to be introduced in following years.A group of 27 employees of a Northfleet firm leapt from the sky to raise money for a local charity.Only 2 of them have parachuted before and 5 had never flown before.
